    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left to give the right owner? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a honest budget-friendly option that could make a great runaround, first car, or tidy little project for someone handy. A straightforward buy for anyone who values value over showroom polish. Priced to sell and ready for its next chapter.",
