      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong project candidate with good bones and a drivetrain that still shows promise. Engine starts, transmission engages, and the car offers a solid foundation for a budget build, parts car, or weekend revival. Cosmetic wear, age-related flaws, and overall rough-condition needs are present, but the chassis feels like a worthwhile platform for someone who knows their way around a toolbox. If you want an affordable entry point into ownership with real potential, this one is worth a look.",
