      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with loads of personality, this car has the kind of honest, lived-in character that turns heads for all the right reasons. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for someone who loves a hands-on project, a weekend fixer, or simply wants an affordable ride with soul. There\u2019s a rugged charm here you just can\u2019t fake\u2014something that feels ready for its next chapter with the right owner behind the wheel. If you appreciate potential, presence, and a price that leaves room to make it your own, this one is easy to imagine bringing back to life.",
